# Uploads Directory

This directory stores user-uploaded files.

## Important

- This directory is excluded from git (see .gitignore)
- Make sure this directory has write permissions
- In production, consider using cloud storage (S3, etc.)

## Local Development

Files uploaded through the API will be stored here.

## Production

For production deployments, configure cloud storage:
- AWS S3
- Google Cloud Storage
- Azure Blob Storage
- Cloudinary

Update the backend configuration to use the appropriate storage service.
